title: Science National Honors Society
description: The Science National Honour Society (SNHS) in our school is a group that celebrates and supports students' accomplishments in science and promotes the quest for scientific understanding. It mainly works at the high school level and gives pupils chances to participate in various science-related extracurricular activities
